      @Modifying @Query(value=" DELETE FROM qds_thread_to_object tto\n USING qds_thread t JOIN qds_event e ON t.id = e.thread_id\n WHERE tto.thread_id = t.id\n AND event_type IN (\'FORK_OUT\',\'JOIN_OUT\')\n AND event_time >= :time\n AND tto.object_id = ANY(:objectIds)\n", nativeQuery=true) void deleteObjectConnectionsToThreadsAfterTime(@Param("time") Integer time, @Param("objectIds") Integer[] objectIds)

    • getAvailableObjects

      @Query(value="SELECT\n o.id,\n o.name,\n o.template_id,\n o.object_type_id,\n o.origin_thread_id\nFROM qds_object o\n JOIN qds_thread_to_object tto ON o.id = tto.object_id\nWHERE o.scenario_id = :scenarioId\n AND (\n o.origin_thread_id = 0\n OR (\n :threadId IS NULL\n OR tto.thread_id = :threadId\n )\n )\nGROUP BY o.id, o.name, o.template_id, o.object_type_id, o.origin_thread_id;\n", nativeQuery=true) List<InternalObjectInstance> getAvailableObjects(@Param("scenarioId") Integer scenarioId, @Param("threadId") Integer threadId)
